Package org.maxicp.cp.examples

Class TSPTW.TSPTWSolution

java.lang.Object
org.maxicp.cp.examples.TSPTW.TSPTWSolution
Enclosing class:
TSPTW
public static class TSPTW.TSPTWSolution extends Object
A solution. To create one, first do new TSPTWSolution, then add, in order, the id of the node being visited addVisit(int) You can also add the whole ordering in one go setVisitOrder(int[]) Do not add the first nor the last stop to the depot, it is implicit

You can check the validity of your solution with compute(), which returns the total distance and throws a RuntimeException if something is invalid or isValid(), which only tells if the solution is valid or not

DO NOT MODIFY THIS CLASS.
